headline: Corn futures tumble following WASDE report
summary: Investing.com -- Corn futures plunged Tuesday after the USDA’s latest World Agricultural Supply and Demand Estimates (WASDE) report projected record U.S. corn production, while agricultural equipment stocks edged lower.
